      "name": "04 - Audit Archive",
      "description": "US-1.Audit-Lean: Query the permanent, immutable retention audit trail.\n\nCovers:\n- List all events (no filter)\n- Filter by pattern A / B\n- Filter by category and sub-category\n- Filter by event type\n- Filter by date range\n- Verify Pattern B events written by trigger",
